/on_select
SNP is required to perform check for serviceability & inventory, for the /select request, and return appropriate response as shown below;
order quote should comply with the following:
all product prices (title_type "item") should have both total & unit prices;
precision for all prices in quote can be up to 2 decimals;
order value, i.e. quote.price.value = Σ quote.breakup[].price.value;
total price for an item should match the unit price for the item * quantity for the item in the quote;
quote provided here is not frozen until /on_init;
