Scenario 2 - Return with liquidation
Return of items can only be initiated:
within the return window for the item (as defined in the catalog);
when fulfillment state, corresponding to item, is "Order-delivered";
Return with liquidation can transition through either of the following state changes:
Scenario A - Return liquidated:
Return_Initiated -> Liquidated (refund triggered here)
Scenario B - Return rejected:
Return_Initiated -> Return_Rejected
If return reason code is invalid, SNP can NACK /update, with error code 30005;
