/on_cancel
SNP can initiate cancellation of order using /on_cancel by setting order state & all fulfillment states to "Cancelled";[g]
SNP can cancel fulfillment using /on_cancel by setting corresponding fulfillment state to "Cancelled";
if cancellation_reason_id is not valid for unsolicited /on_cancel (i.e. not one of the cancellation reasons that can be used by SNP), BNP may NACK /on_cancel with error code 22502;
if updated quote does not match the original order value with the cancellation terms applied, BNP may NACK /on_cancel with error code 22503;
