/on_status
/on_status response can be solicited or unsolicited;
/on_status returns the audit trail for order items (including status of item returns, cancels processed or in-progress), the current state of order items & fulfillments, order quote & breakup:
SNP maintains a copy of the order, which includes the order at /on_confirm and an audit trail of all post-order flow processes;
same order will be returned in any post-order flow callback, such as /on_status, /on_update, /on_cancel;
sample payload below shows order state for normal order and doesn’t include post-order flow processes such as cancel, return, etc;
BNP may send NACK for /on_status with error code for cases such as:
NACK received by seller app for /on_confirm but seller app sends /on_status to update order state to "Accepted";
In case of NACK received for /on_status, SNP should rollback order to previous state of the order, i.e. the state prior to sending /on_status;
