SNP approves return request with state "Return_Approved":
SNP also includes reverse qc input for return pickup check;
BNP creates order for logistics for return pickup;
BNP requests update for fulfillment state, reverse qc output for return fulfillment(see "Status update" above);
BNP will need to factor in return costs;
